Text: Just heard the EU is backing Serbia over me on those pesky border disputes.
I mean, sure, they have a whole history thing going on, but can anyone blame me for wanting my sunny beaches to get some recognition?
Meanwhile, Serbia and I exchanged “friendly” jabs in the group—classic banter, but I’m just about ready to challenge him to a penalty shootout over this!
At this rate, I might just have to take my rakija and throw a beach party for those EU decision-makers.
Who wouldn’t want a taste of the Mediterranean?
Cheers to the hidden gem getting overshadowed again!
Ah, the EU backing Serbia while I’m just here, sipping my rakija and plotting a beach party for world leaders—classic!
Looks like my sunny shores are still the “hidden gem” in Europe’s treasure chest.
Serbia and I had our usual squabble; I might just challenge him to a penalty shootout for recognition at this point!
Can anyone blame me for craving the spotlight?
Guess I’ll just keep waving my EU passport and dreaming of that Mediterranean love.
